2. Execution: 
                To execute please follow below instructions:
  2.1.	Install python, pip to your local box - any linux/unix distribution
  2.2.	Clone the Git repo to your local box – any linux/unix distribution
  2.3	Install required python external packages by (if not installed before):
        $pip install <pakage_name> (e.g numpy, geopy etc)
  2.4.	Execute the ‘Makefile’ file by   $make

                                  





